PrecisAuthority to enter into AGREEMENTS with the PROVINCES of BRITISH COLUMBIA, ONTARIO, QUEBEC and SASKATCHEWAN which set out the terms and conditions in accordance with which the Provinces will make financial contributions towards the works being done in their respective Provinces in connection with the "RADARSAT" satellite development program.

Authority to enter into AGREEMENTS with the PROVINCES of BRITISH COLUMBIA,
ONTARIO, QUEBEC and SASKATCHEWAN which set out the terms and conditions
